  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6519.98 sitting just below the massive negative gamma wall at 6500 (-9.6B), dealers are positioned to amplify any downward move toward 6500, creating accelerated selling pressure if that level breaks. The PIN regime with positive gamma dominance above current levels means dealers will fade moves higher into the 6525-6545 zone, capping upside momentum as they sell into strength. Watch 6500 as the critical fulcrum - a break below triggers dealer selling into the void, while any bounce gets met with systematic selling pressure at 6525+ where positive gamma concentration peaks.",
